==English==
{{wikipedia}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#{{botany}} a member of the [[Bryophyta]] (in the broadest sense). Any [[plant]] in which the [[gametophyte]] ([[haploid]]) stage of the lifecycle is the larger, persistent stage, and the [[sporophyte]] ([[diploid]]) stage is small and dependent upon the [[gametophyte]].  Bryophytes include [[moss]]es, [[liverwort]]s, and [[hornwort]]s.

